{"tid":2401757,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"指大律師公會知悉,夏博義反駁689：早辭英議席","createTime":"2021-02-10T03:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T07:40:56.000Z","uid":239336,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"92ecbf75724a57425bf8e7416bcb7f1243f2afd5","tid":2401757,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】新任大律師公會主席夏博義（Paul Harris）早前提出修改港版國安法主張後，先後遭到港澳辦、中聯辦、中共官媒及全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英圍攻，梁振英更發公開信，指他曾任英國牛津市議員，再任公會主席是「荒天下之大謬」。夏博義回覆本報查詢時反駁，梁對他及公會的評論不公平及不準確，強調遭不公平攻擊後獲得強勁支持，故有更大決心做好大律師公會主席工作。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英昨日發表的公開信中，引述《星島日報》昨日的報道，指提名夏博義參選大律師公會主席的資深大律師駱應淦，亦是昨日才得知夏博義曾經出任英國牛津巿議員，又指他身兼英國自由民主黨成員，其政治背景對於近年變得政治化的大律師公會，以及其會員並無幫助，更指夏博義的主席地位已被損害和站不住腳，要求他考慮辭職。<br />\n<br />\n夏博義指大律師公會在他當選主席前已知悉他曾任英國巿議員，亦清楚他在獲提名參選時已辭去相關職務。他更透露，受到包括梁振英在內的連串不公平攻擊後，獲得很多強勁的支持，對此感到十分感動，並認為上述支持令他有更大決心，在任期內做好大律師公會主席的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/UQ3OJ7PEVJFYTCKCZVLFH6HKGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FUQ3OJ7PEVJFYTCKCZVLFH6HKGI%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQlScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=3946ee81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FUQ3OJ7PEVJFYTCKCZVLFH6HKGI%2F&h=8837aee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/UQ3OJ7PEVJFYTCKCZVLFH6HKGI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c629d648d43bddc3b0f6826c46785edb8b213e","tid":2401757,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab84580aa8b1baf250fe3b536e922287050af3c3","tid":2401757,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f866f452115c5b4c445d4a5b06b90c40f44b6b5","tid":2401757,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a8dd6b4fa32c0cc5d9c144108cc0fb19f2c7dd","tid":2401757,"uid":89316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"689啲9up係藍絲先信到十足 邏輯混亂專打稻草人"}]}